How to create a class of something or how to create an object in real life

1. create the class
2. create the object of the class like property,attributes,fields
3. create the method,behaviours and function of the class
4. create your main method
5. create the object of the class to access it
6. example how we create the class and the property and method and main method and access them

class Human{
String name;
String color;
int age;
// now here we create the method of our class like the behaviour of our class what our class can do
void eat(){
System.out.println("human eat");
}
void talk(){
System.out.println("human talking");
}
// we creat our main method
public static void main (System[]args){
// then we create the object of our class how we can access them
// we write the class name first then name the = sign then new key word then name of the class ();
Human human=new Human();
// then acess them
human.name="ahamad";
human.color="white";
human.age=30;

// then we what to see the result we sout that like this name then .
System.out.println(human.name);
// to access the method we create the object of it
human.eat();
}
}